{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-project-template-js","path":"/projects/boards-and-commissions/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2>Project Overview</h2>\n<p>As part of modernizing boston.gov, we're slowly going through the legacy web applications we have left on cityofboston.gov and moving each over to <a href=\"https://www.boston.gov/\">boston.gov</a>.</p>\n<p>We thought it was important to make the information our boards and commissions look-up tool displays easier to find on boston.gov, so we updated the app and integrated the information it displayed into boston.gov.</p>\n<p>To display the data, we built custom Drupal components that contect to the database where the information is managed by our Clerk's Office. We also gave each board/commission its own boston.gov page, empowering staff to add additional information like meeting minutes and agendas. Our <a href=\"https://www.boston.gov/departments/public-facilities/public-facilities-commission\">Public Facilities Commission</a> is a good example of this idea at work.</p>\n<p>We wrote more about these updates and our process on the Digital Team's blog: <a href=\"https://www.boston.gov/news/boards-and-commissions-get-deserved-bostongov-facelift\">Boards and Commissions get a deserved boston.gov facelift</a>.</p>\n<h2>Quicklinks</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.boston.gov/news/boards-and-commissions-get-deserved-bostongov-facelift\">Blog post</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.boston.gov/civic-engagement/boards-and-commissions\">Updated board and commission search page</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.boston.gov/historic-district/back-bay-architectural-district#commission-information\">The new components on boston.gov</a></li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<div class=\"imageBlock\">\n    <div>\n        <a href=\"https://www.boston.gov/news/boards-and-commissions-get-deserved-bostongov-facelift\">\n            <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 900px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 52.44444444444445%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"Boards and Commissions get a deserved boston.gov facelift\" title=\"Boards and Commissions get a deserved boston.gov facelift\" src=\"/static/165167fee25547fee067658dc230e718/1cfc2/boards-commissions-screen-shot.png\" srcset=\"/static/165167fee25547fee067658dc230e718/3684f/boards-commissions-screen-shot.png 225w,\n/static/165167fee25547fee067658dc230e718/fc2a6/boards-commissions-screen-shot.png 450w,\n/static/165167fee25547fee067658dc230e718/1cfc2/boards-commissions-screen-shot.png 900w,\n/static/165167fee25547fee067658dc230e718/21482/boards-commissions-screen-shot.png 1350w,\n/static/165167fee25547fee067658dc230e718/d61c2/boards-commissions-screen-shot.png 1800w,\n/static/165167fee25547fee067658dc230e718/d9ed5/boards-commissions-screen-shot.png 2880w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n    </span>\n        </a>\n    </div>\n</div>","frontmatter":{"title":"Boards and Commissions","myRole":"Product Manager"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/projects/boards-and-commissions/"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}